script.name: lib.cycrow.getloadoutsetting
script.sourceplaintext:
$table.lookup = table alloc
$ignore = [FALSE] $new.string = null $new.value = null
if $a.setting == 'marine.board' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=116 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'wingman' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=58 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'autojump' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=50 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'notify' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=45 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'emergency.jump' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=52 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'property.hidden' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=86 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'property.favourite' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=115 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'drop.drones' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=134 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'ignore.blacklist' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=130 gosub sub.DoBoolean else if $a.setting == 'autojump.fuel' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=54 gosub sub.DoInteger else if $a.setting == 'autojump.range' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=51 gosub sub.DoInteger else if $a.setting == 'emergency.jump.shields' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=53 gosub sub.DoPercent else if $a.setting == 'formation' $new.string = 'Formation' $list = array alloc: size=8 $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=10 $list[0] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=11 $list[1] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=12 $list[2] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=13 $list[3] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=14 $list[4] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=15 $list[5] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=16 $list[6] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=17 $list[7] = $read.text gosub sub.DoList else if $a.setting == 'attacked.response' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=133 $list = array alloc: size=4 $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=100 $list[0] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=101 $list[1] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=102 $list[2] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=2012 id=103 $list[3] = $read.text gosub sub.DoList else if $a.setting == 'wing' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=47 gosub sub.DoObject else if $a.setting == 'homebase' $new.string = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=8 gosub sub.DoObject else if $a.setting == 'fleet.leader' $new.string = 'Fleet Leader' gosub sub.DoObject else if $a.setting == 'turret.1' $turret = 1 gosub sub.DoTurret else if $a.setting == 'turret.2' $turret = 2 gosub sub.DoTurret else if $a.setting == 'turret.3' $turret = 3 gosub sub.DoTurret else if $a.setting == 'turret.4' $turret = 4 gosub sub.DoTurret else if $a.setting == 'turret.5' $turret = 5 gosub sub.DoTurret else if $a.setting == 'turret.6' $turret = 6 gosub sub.DoTurret end
if $new.string $ret = create new array, arguments=$new.string, $new.value, null, null, null else if $ignore $ret = [NULL] else $ret = create new array, arguments=$a.setting, $a.value, null, null, null end return $ret
sub.DoBoolean: if $a.value $new.value = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102301 else $new.value = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102302 end endsub
sub.DoInteger: skip if $a.value $a.value = 0 $new.value = convert number $a.value to string endsub
sub.DoPercent: skip if $a.value $a.value = 0 $new.value = convert number $a.value to string $new.value = sprintf: fmt='%s%%', $new.value, null, null, null, null endsub
sub.DoObject: if $a.value -> exists $new.value = $a.value -> get name else $new.value = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=676 end endsub
sub.DoList: $list.size = size of array $list if $a.value >= 0 AND $a.value < $list.size $new.value = $list[$a.value] end endsub
sub.DoLookup: $new.value = $table.lookup[$a.value] endsub
sub.DoTurret: $turret.count = get number of turrets: shiptype=$a.shiptype if $turret < $turret.count $new.value = get command name: command=$a.value $text = get turret text: shiptype=$a.shiptype turret=$turret $read.text = read text: page=[Page.CmdConsole] id=12 $new.string = sprintf: fmt='%s: %s', $read.text, $text, null, null, null else $ignore = [TRUE] end endsub
return null
